& [ResearchFindings] is the extracted theorem boundary
  + [finding_001] is the official proof has two linked jobs
    = meaning: construct the four-dimensional quantum Yang-Mills theory and prove a positive mass gap in that constructed theory
  + [finding_002] is the Euclidean route has a recognizable pipeline
    = meaning: define Euclidean correlation functions or measure, prove OS-type properties, reconstruct Hilbert space and Hamiltonian, then prove spectral gap
  + [finding_003] is lattice gauge theory supplies evidence and approximating frameworks
    = meaning: lattice constructions and numerical/simulation results can motivate a gap but do not by themselves give the continuum Millennium proof
  + [finding_004] is mass gap can be studied through exponential decay of Euclidean correlations
    = meaning: a positive spectral gap should correspond to sufficiently strong correlation decay after reconstruction
  + [finding_005] is uniform control in the continuum/volume limit is a central hard lock
    = meaning: strong-coupling, finite-lattice, or bounded-volume gap evidence must survive the limiting process with required axioms intact
  + [finding_006] is recent unaccepted claimed solutions are not authority
    = meaning: claimed arXiv/preprint/independent proofs remain outside unless accepted by the mathematical community or checked rigorously in-project

& [RouteMap] is the construction pipeline
  + [stage_001_regularized_model] is define lattice, cutoff, finite-volume, or other regularized Yang-Mills model
  + [stage_002_uniform_estimates] is obtain bounds independent of cutoff and volume sufficient for a continuum limit
  + [stage_003_limit_measure_or_correlators] is construct continuum Euclidean Schwinger functions or measure
  + [stage_004_os_axioms] is prove Euclidean invariance, symmetry, reflection positivity, regularity, and clustering as needed
  + [stage_005_reconstruction] is reconstruct Wightman theory, Hilbert space, fields or observables, and Hamiltonian
  + [stage_006_nontriviality] is show the theory is interacting/nontrivial
  + [stage_007_gap] is prove positive spectral gap or exponential correlation decay strong enough to imply it

& [SymbolicTranslation] is the adjusted source mapping
  + [sealed_curvature] maps_to possible nonperturbative confinement/gap intuition, not construction
  + [curvature_packet] maps_to gauge-invariant massive excitation or glueball intuition, not a defined state without reconstruction
  + [phase_key] maps_to possible change of variables, duality, or invariant observable if formalized
  + [symbolic_encryption] maps_to nonperturbative inaccessibility, not a mathematical object
  + [resistance_to_unfolding] maps_to spectral gap or exponential decay only after a theory and Hamiltonian/correlators exist

& [PropositionAdjustment] is the new Yang-Mills shape
  + [old_claim] is mass gap emerges from symbolic sealed curvature
  + [adjusted_claim] is sealed curvature can only become proof-relevant if it supplies a constructive mechanism for uniform continuum estimates, OS reconstruction, nontriviality, or exponential decay/spectral gap
  + [promising_direction] is investigate whether source language resembles a duality/change-of-variables heuristic for nonperturbative gap formation
  + [open_lock] is no rigorous regularized-to-continuum construction with uniform gap control is supplied
  + [solution_potential] is low as proof, moderate as heuristic for classifying gap mechanisms

